{"type": "article", "id": 38700, "title": "Chloé任命新的创意总监，以及，VSCO推出Gif拍摄｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-03-13T03:13:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 968, "name": "IPO"}, {"id": 1581, "name": "Chloe"}, {"id": 35943, "name": "加拿大鹅"}, {"id": 38460, "name": "最有价值的服装品牌"}, {"id": 38461, "name": "B&O PLAY"}, {"id": 38462, "name": "无线蓝牙耳机"}, {"id": 36328, "name": "Frank Ocean"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170313112004PWlXsQBYEdRqUK4y.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/canada-goose-ipo-expected-next-week-fashion-scoops-10842348/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>加拿大鹅将于下周 IPO</strong></a> | 高端羽绒服品牌 Canada Goose 将于下周同时登陆纽约和多伦多的证券市场，计划募资 3 亿美元，股票代码 GOOS。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/chloe-natacha-ramsay-levi-creative-director-10841690/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Chloé 任命新的创意总监</strong></a> | 在今年一月，Chloé 的前创意总监，英国设计师 Clare Waight Keller 离职后，Chloé 确认该职位将由 Natacha Ramsay-Levi 来接任。Natacha 之前曾与设计师 Nicolas Ghesquiere 共事，在 LV 的女装成衣部门工作，更早之前与 Chesquiere 一起服务于 Balenciaga。Natacha 的任命将于 4 月 3 日起生效，她将在今年九月发布上任后的首秀—— Chloé 2018 春夏系列。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/bo-play-beoplay-h4-headphones\" rel=\"nofollow\">B&amp;O PLAY 发布了全新的 Beoplay H4 无线耳机</a>。这款耳机由丹麦设计师 Jakob Wagner 操刀打造，外型使用了小羊皮、编织物与铝金属，保留了 B&amp;O PLAY 的简约风格。另外，它还有简单直观的用户交互设计，包含三个按钮、一个微型 USB 接口和 3.5mm 转接口，定价为 2298 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101929buGjmc06xv18Kknl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101929TaZkJmwoiVGM1bYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101941Voe08IRnrptmMCcY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101941pRWx5XKsGtqw0Qnz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/nike-free-inneva-wvn-motion\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 推出了全新 Free Inneva WVN Motion 编织结构跑鞋</a>，这款跑鞋采用了尼龙编织和 Nike Free 鞋底，在鞋舌与后跟处加入了高质感皮革，将于 3 月 16 日登陆 Solebox 发售，定价为 180 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101842fFzSZN9Tw6BvxLp2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101842TNtP93deqOrlvhJF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.672727\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101842mVUTaej7L1uCt2zw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101842gv9R8MHVwZsahrn3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101853nev2Cql3rwoLiVQ1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101914z1MRFlHfX2acVmZG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/atmos-air-jordan-air-max-pack-release-date\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 与 Jordan Brand 联手，推出 atmos Air Jordan Air Max Pack</a>。该套装中包括一双经典的 Air Jordan 3，结合了橙色细节及半透明蓝色外底，另一双 Air Max 1 在设计上与 Air Max Day 版本有些许差别，换上了 Elephant 图案的鞋垫，并将 Nike 与 Jumpman Logo 分别点缀于左右。</p><p>另外，它还配备了特别定制的两种图案拼接鞋盒，极具收藏价值，定价为 400 美元，将于 3 月 18 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101405oC2NJmWkgOd5zv7t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101433nbLptSih0xlAZsU1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101433cCPlmSIqhuigBtZN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101433ZFC3YdJy7D5EieoV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101433uN9HIoA0kciV62ea.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101433X1PUmNq7W2F6lgSe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101541OUp2askomeiDGFtu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101541fEihudnL5eDO3akt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703131015405vIgteRGMQa7b6o1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101551iVLnaWylITtQUg7f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101558q4Jm7btRyfLe1Ol2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101558guWCS7OsJELVtAMX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101611ryOiMos5du1WaqXY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/vsco-will-bring-gifs-to-ios\" rel=\"nofollow\">手机修图软件 VSCO 更新，推出了 GIF 拍摄功能</a>，可以直接在拍摄功能中切换拍摄 GIF。不过，目前只有 iOS 版推出了更新功能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101619JnMYDRU087otkqj5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/hero-magazine-supreme-x-louis-vuitton-editorial\" rel=\"nofollow\">最新一期的男装时尚杂志《HERO》，发布 Louis Vuitton x Supreme 联名系列造型特辑</a>。特辑围绕着 Dangerous Youth 的主题，展示了蓝色牛仔外套、棕色 Monogram 围巾、红色 Supreme Box Logo 挎包以及致敬艺术家 Andy Warhol 的腰包等单品。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703131018151acVgdwjnDhpL6Xx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101816b5tFMjz7mqvHY12I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101825B7t6FSg8sGqCpc54.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101825GWuH74bi6mYsNoRy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Frank Ocean 联合 A$AP Rocky，发布全新单曲《Chanel》，来<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/11/frank-ocean-chanel-asap-rocky-remix/\" rel=\"nofollow\">听听看</a>： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170313101724LKv7PJTHgFcV38oW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/3/bo-play-beoplay-h4-headphones\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}